rule.constraints:
- Replace \mathrm{MSE} with \text{MSE}
- Replace \mathrm{SE} with \text{SE}
- Replace \mathrm{eff} with \text{eff}
- Replace \mathrm{Cov} with \text{Cov}
- Prose in Math: If \mbox{} contains standard English words or phrases inside an equation, replace it with \text{}.
- Math Operators: If \mbox{} contains a mathematical operator, function, or semantic label, replace it with \operatorname{} or \text{} as appropriate to ensure semantic screen reader tagging.
